### teaching-animation 可再生的构建产物
# 成片/动图: 跑 render.sh / build_video.sh 可重出
skills/linyuebanzi-teaching-animation/examples/**/renders/
skills/linyuebanzi-teaching-animation/examples/outputs/
# TTS 音频: 跑 minimax_tts.py 可重出 (durations.json 保留, 是时间轴参考)
skills/linyuebanzi-teaching-animation/examples/**/audio/*.mp3
# Manim 渲染缓存 / 蒙太奇临时帧
skills/linyuebanzi-teaching-animation/**/media/
skills/linyuebanzi-teaching-animation/**/preview/.frames/
# 测试运行的示例项目 (canonical 示例只保留 sound-video / sound_phenomena.py)
skills/linyuebanzi-teaching-animation/examples/ohms-law-video/
skills/linyuebanzi-teaching-animation/examples/pythagorean-video/
